{"tid":2165984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我宣佈，我決定加入民建聯","createTime":"2020-08-20T07:04:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T07:30:41.000Z","uid":12773,"like":10,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"62ee53994aef870c22cd6b217394ed7ee0c4ef67","tid":2165984,"uid":12773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T07:04:12.000Z","msg":"為左乜？<br />\n為左維穩<br />\n為左蛇齋餅糭<br />\n為左錢<br />\n為左生活<br />\n<br />\n我知道大家都會有少少失望<br />\n但人不為己 天誅地滅<br />\n我會用比較科學化既民調<br />\n決定我既去向<br />\n而呢個民調<br />\n當然唔會係連登，高登，FB，Instagram 進行<br />\n我既民調對象會係香討，babykingdom<br />\n係屋邨樓下賭緊錢同捉緊棋既老坑<br />\n同埋各建制中人<br />\n務求得出一個公平公正的民調結果<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好屌我負評我<br />\n就算我殺人放火出賣香港人都好<br />\n記住我哋口號<br />\n<br />\n不分化<br />\n不割蓆"},{"pid":"0beddb8f2b103b282f921500505a837acd414cc7","tid":2165984,"uid":12773,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T07:04:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e116dfb6e3e9ed2fe2d3579fee5fa36b43c391d","tid":2165984,"uid":176282,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T07:04:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a91f84215f6bb462401de71b875407895a253b2a","tid":2165984,"uid":12773,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T07:04:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"